Data-RuledValidator

Data::RuledValidator is validator of data.
This needs rule which is readable by not programmer,
which is like a specification.
Data::RuledValidator parse the rule and check validation.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module plugins requires these other modules and libraries:

 Email::Valid
 Email::Valid::Loose

